sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  actor Driver
  participant App as Driver App
  participant Gateway as API Gateway
  participant Auth as Auth Guard
  participant DriverSvc as Driver Service
  participant Redis as Redis GEO
  participant Socket as Socket.IO
  Driver->>App: Toggle ONLINE
  App->>Gateway: POST /api/drivers/me/availability
  Gateway->>Auth: Verify DRIVER JWT
  Auth-->>Gateway: Authorized
  Gateway->>DriverSvc: Set availability ONLINE with GPS
  DriverSvc->>DriverSvc: Check approval, vehicle, wallet policy
  alt Eligible and GPS valid
    DriverSvc->>Redis: GEOADD drivers:geo:online
    DriverSvc-->>Gateway: ONLINE
    Gateway->>Socket: Join driver online room
    Gateway-->>App: Online status accepted
  else Not eligible
    DriverSvc-->>Gateway: Reject with reason
    Gateway-->>App: Show reason
  end
  loop Periodic location ping
    App->>Gateway: PATCH /api/drivers/me/location
    Gateway->>DriverSvc: Update location
    DriverSvc->>Redis: GEOADD latest location
  end
  Driver->>App: Toggle OFFLINE
  App->>Gateway: POST /api/drivers/me/availability OFFLINE
  Gateway->>DriverSvc: Set availability OFFLINE
  DriverSvc->>Redis: ZREM drivers:geo:online
  Gateway->>Socket: Leave online room
  Gateway-->>App: Offline status accepted
